Race.Name: Atmosphere
Race.Description: You can still remember watching that rocket launch on TV and wh ispering with excitement ''Mommy, can I be an astronaut?'' And when mommy pointed out that you were a 35-year-old morbidly obe se junkie living in her basement, you felt that beautiful dream die a little. Well, time to suit up and show them you're never too old or underqualified to burn up on reentry. Point to poin t race for the Rocket Voltic.
